In the next video,
we'll talk about how

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:33.916
you have to the right amount
of the hormone or else things

00:09:33.916 --> 00:09:34.530
go awry.

00:09:34.530 --> 00:09:34.960
SALMAN KHAN: Very cool.

